sources.description:
Kruty 1918 - Ukraine, 1918. In an act of bravery, a unit of 300 men, mostly students, gather at the train station of Kruty in an effort to block the advance of a Bolshevik army of 4000 strong. Outnumbered by over 10-1, the young men put their very lives on the line in order to protect Kiev from being overrun.
2019.  Stars: Maksim Donets, Andrey Fedinchik, Alina Kovalenko
